COMMITTEE AMENDMENT

COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to S.P. 10
315 The amendment also adds a provision that directs any delegates to a convention called for
326 as a result of this application to be limited to considering and proposing amendments within
337 the scope of the application.
